<br>
1. Is it true the Queen in chardok is on Collective faction?<br>
<br>
2. Does Warlord Skargus summon? (i.e. 51+?)<br>
<br>
Thanks <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ullliry.showPublicProfile?language=EN>llliry</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/26/01 3:12:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> clues.</span><hr size=1> I think that shoulders/arms/wrist item is a side quest. The 3rd ring quest is a whole diffrent story. I talked with few people on diffrent servers and the 3rd ring is like 10 ac, 90hp/mana, +some other stats, effect: flowing thought II.<br>
<br>
All i have about the quest are some directions, nothing concrete. I got tips to focus on thing between overking, prince, Korocust and the acused sanark.<br>
<br>
Hope this will lead to somewhere.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Neverending misfit of ol' Sol Ro school. <br>
Illiry<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uzania.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zania</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/26/01 3:22:28 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: clues.</span><hr size=1> If the queen eats the 2nd ring when given with 2 items she requestes I would think it to be a continuation not a sidequest.  And from what I read queen offers you to advance further when hailed, that also leads me to believe that its the next step instead of subquest.  <br>
<br>
Zania <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufireblade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fireblade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/26/01 3:23:43 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: clues.</span><hr size=1> She asks for the 2nd ring only as proof of loyalty.  And gives it back after.  If it was a continuation, she probably wouldn't give you the ring back, that's why it seems like a side quest. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utadenea.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tadenea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/26/01 6:45:58 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: clues.</span><hr size=1> the Warlord you must kill for second ring is level 57 Sk so yes he will summon<br>
we were able to kill him with 1 group and thats with only 1 healer a druid <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uirdanar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Irdanar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/26/01 8:19:53 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: clues.</span><hr size=1> Illry, where did you get that information, and can you get proof?<br>
<br>
I find it hard to believe they'd do such a minor bump from 2nd to 3rd ring, and change the effect entirely like that.<br>
<br>
Also, if there is a third ring, where did they begin it? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ureegor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Reegor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/27/01 2:52:04 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re:  Iksar faction</span><hr size=1> It really dosn't seem like Iksars should be able to get to ally with Di'Zok but I am willing to bet money that they can.  I know when they first put in the ally faction, I was able to get to ally with the North Freeport pallys... then one day I was probably a few hits below ally without takeing any faction hits in either direction so I went to go kill an orc... and sure enough... my max cap was moved below ally.  Probably just barely.<br>
<br>
So they do have race dependant faction caps, or so it seems... but I plan on finding out for myself if an Iksar can become ally with the brood of Di'Zok. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukareksiss.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kareksiss</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/27/01 2:58:46 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re:  Iksar faction</span><hr size=1> i estimate i'm at roughly 2k faction hits currently, should see if i can raise it good or not.  Here's to hoping i havent wasted 25 hours of Droga killin heheh. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ureegor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Reegor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/27/01 5:55:31 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Iksar faction</span><hr size=1> Even if it caps at dubious, can't do the quests.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Seriously doubt you're wasteing time though.  Actually, I am suprised that I don't see any bad Cab faction hits anywhere here.  Especialy when you cut off the supply of goblin slaves, you'd think that would piss some Iksar off somewhere, eh? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukareksiss.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kareksiss</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/27/01 6:35:56 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Iksar faction</span><hr size=1> Well, after just about forever, i'm at Threateningly.  Hopefully i'll find the time in the next few days to see how high it goes and let yas know.  If an Iksar can go from max KoS to ally, then ANYONE can.  On a highlight, i'm up to 2 idols so far from this monotony : ) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uskrilmo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Skrilmo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/27/01 10:12:13 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Iksar faction</span><hr size=1> if you use all the charges on ring 2, does it get recharged when you get it back from the queen? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uirdanar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Irdanar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/27/01 10:33:40 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Iksar faction</span><hr size=1> Ikasr can go to Ally, I'm proof.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uctiz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ctiz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/27/01 12:40:38 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Iksar faction</span><hr size=1> /agree, Iksar can be ally.  I am currently ally in Chardok and hvae my 2nd ring. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pu